{"tid":985434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★政Whats噏：游蕙禎po十年前舊照　網民問邊位？","createTime":"2019-01-17T14:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T11:18:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":40,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bea2ae12c101b0c6907d91f72c0beed7e047ad80","tid":985434,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/photo/bkn-20190117155107573-0117_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190117174115\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190117155107573-0117_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190117174115&h=68d9b1b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日潮玩10YearChallenge，唔少政界人士都攞咗自己十年前同依家嘅近照出嚟對比，被DQ立法會議員資格嘅青年新政游蕙禎上載咗十年前嘅相，相中人着住紅色格仔衫，一臉稚氣，唔少網民直呼「邊位呀？」由於佢仲攞咗張嘔吐白沬嘅黑貓出嚟代表依家嘅自己，有網民形容佢變咗死貓。<br />\n<br />\n唔少政界人士都跟貼潮流，好似游蕙禎咁，尋晚喺Facebook上載咗張相之後，已經吸引唔少網友留言，雖然有網民唔認得佢，但亦有留言話佢女大十八變，有網友讚依家靚過十年前，仲有人話認得佢着嗰件格仔衫，就係佢經常出席論壇時着嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117155107573-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fbkn-20190117155107573-0117_00822_001.html&d=IXeaUj7MBsH%2FpAjUoWaQHNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=54abbd60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117155107573-0117_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c87b5bcd53b3bae0ac6629da9c49a2e4ac782128","tid":985434,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e0d47a6728796b83ccccdf6dc11d362fd1cb6c","tid":985434,"uid":147361,"like":121,"dislike":3,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:44:4